replies.txt_content: 标题: chestcommands的问题为啥用chestcommands做商店，收购物品这个，要是没有物品就会报错，求解决

replies.author: 爱心魔王FHC
replies.txt_content: 这是服务器问题么，如果是就错版了

replies.author: pva1010
replies.txt_content:
我的服务器在前几天也出现了这个问题，服务器是1.7.2mod服。仔细翻看后台记录后发现有这句话：[ChestCommands] Could not find a compatible NMS code for this bukkit version. Attributes will show up on items. If you're using a new version ,expect an update soon. The plugin will still work.
意思大概是，需要将插件更换版本，才可以兼容你当前的服务器
